    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Currently</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-700">
        <li>
          üìç Recently graduated from Wabash College with a B.A in Computer
          Science and Studio Art!
        </li>
        <li>
          üíª I am passionate about working on software aimed to solve real-world
          problems
        </li>
        <li>‚úÇÔ∏è Continuing to pursue and improve my barbering skills</li>
        <li>
          ü•Å Love playing the drums and am currently exploring Jazz drumming!
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
          Featured Project: Montgomery County Free Clinic Intake System
        </h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
          Built a fully functional bilingual patient intake for the Montgomery
          County Free Clinic using React, TypeScript, and SQL. Designed to
          reduce friction and improve accessibility for both patients and staff.
        </p>
        <p>
          Features include multi-step forms, real-time validation, data
          persistence, and an intuitive UI optimized for speed and ease of use.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/projects"
          class="inline-block rounded-xl bg-black px-6 py-3 text-white font-medium hover:bg-neutral-800"
        >
          View all projects
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="aspect-video overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border bg-neutral-100"
      >
        <img
          src="/moco.png"
          alt="Clinic Intake System screenshot"
          class="h-full w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 border-t">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-lg font-medium">
        Thank you for visiting my personal site! more sections and improvements
        coming soon.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
